 Titled Lockdown, the new Mzansi Magic series is set in a fictional high security female prison.The novice show is billed as tough, terse, gripping and the channel s edgiest drama series to date.The Orange is the New Black-esque show will feature back-stories that will unravel to reveal the paths that led the characters behind locked gates.Scheduled to premi re in January 2017; Zola Nombona, Luxolo Ndabeni, Nomsa Buthelezi, Lindiwe Ndlovu and Mthunzi Ntoyi complete the star-studded cast.